{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0002", "text": "Many entrepreneurs wonder: Why do I need to check my suppliers?", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0002", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0003", "text": "It may feel uncomfortable and may affect the collaboration.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0003", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0004", "text": "Yet the figures show why this is so important.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0004", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0005", "text": "Research by the Institute for Associations, Industries and Professions (IVBB) shows that most cyber attacks occur via suppliers and the supply chain:. 1. Suppliers and supply chains – 40.1%\n2. Own technology with vulnerabilities – 35.8%\n3. Own employees (errors) – 24.1%. So many of the successful cyber attacks come through suppliers. That is why it is crucial to make clear agreements with them about cybersecurity. Which sectors are most attacked? Some sectors are more attractive to cybercriminals than others. These are the top 10 sectors with the most cyber attacks:. 1.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0005", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0006", "text": "Construction – 17%\n2. Manufacturing – 14%\n3. Healthcare – 14%\n4. Retail – 12%\n5. Technology – 11%\n6. Transport – 7%\n7.Legal – 7%\n8. Education – 6%\n9. Financial services – 6%\n10. Automotive – 6%\n11. Other sectors – 23%. Does your company fall on this list? Then it is extra important to arrange your cybersecurity properly and check your suppliers.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0006", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0007", "text": "They can be the weakest link. What can you do? Make clear agreements with suppliers about cybersecurity. Check regularly whether they adhere to these agreements. Assess risks and ensure backups and contingency plans.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0007", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0008", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0008", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0009", "text": "Take cyber measures yourself or report fraud? About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__c6-semantic__0009", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c6-semantic", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 11, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
